main event: A bright, round object with flashing lights was observed passing rapidly overhead from west to east in Folsom, California on April 20, 1964.
interesting points: The object was observed for approximately 10 seconds before disappearing from view.
The object was described as being round and illuminated with a white light.
The object was hovering silently over the area for a short period of time before departing at a high rate of speed.
Two witnesses, a 24-year-old and a 19-year-old, reported seeing the object.
The object was estimated to be traveling at a fast speed.
sighted object: a bright, round object with flashing lights
